com.sap.spe.pricing.transactiondata.userexit

Interface IPricingConditionUserExit

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ICondition, IPricingConditionCommon
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IPricingConditionSAPExit

    public interface IPricingConditionUserExit
extends IPricingConditionCommon
    A pricing condition contains information copied from the pricing knowledge base (from the customizing of the condition type and the pricing procedure), from the condition record, and from the result of the calculation. The methods of this interface can be used in the SPE userexits.
